<section class="farm-story">
  <div class="farm-story__image">
    <img src="{{ 'new-FS-logo.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Cal Poly Pomona Farm Store logo">
  </div>

  <div class="farm-story__content">
    <p class="farm-story__eyebrow">Our Story</p>

    <h2>Rooted in Cal Poly Pomona agriculture.</h2>

    <p>
      The Cal Poly Pomona Farm Store connects the community with fresh produce,
      local goods, dairy products, pantry staples, and seasonal items grown or
      supported through the university’s agricultural programs.
    </p>

    <p>
      This future-state shopping experience highlights the Farm Store’s unique
      position as more than a retail store — it is a local, educational, and
      community-driven destination.
    </p>

    <a href="/pages/about" class="farm-story__btn">
      Learn More
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

